---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Vitaly Executive Chauffeur — how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <section class="pt-40 pb-24 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert prose-gold">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We collect information you provide when making a booking or enquiry, including your name, email address, phone number, and travel details.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>Your information is used solely to arrange and manage your bookings, respond to enquiries, and improve our service. We do not sell or share your data with third parties.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>We retain your personal data only as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes outlined in this policy, or as required by law.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@vitalychauffeur.ie" class="text-gold-400 hover:underline">info@vitalychauffeur.ie</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">5. Contact</h2>
          <p>For any privacy-related queries, contact Vitaly Executive Chauffeur at <a href="mailto:info@vitalychauffeur.ie" class="text-gold-400 hover:underline">info@vitalychauffeur.ie</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
